stanimations.com/Fantasy/Mages/Druid-03.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Derakor the Vindicator</span><hr size=1> Its not us that needs to do 1k DPS.  Vindi does 1k DPS.  Until we are sure we can keep a tank alive to suck up that much damage, this is pretty much out of reach. <p><br><center><a href="http://www.unhomed.com">
