<br>
to be MT for vindi, it's a good idea to have 6000hp's.  An even better situation would be to have both me and Vigdis at that point, so if one of us fell, the other steps in.  However, 750hp upgrades aren't easy to come by <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   So rather than rely on a tank, we have to rely on the CH rotation - I will work on Legion's rotation, and i suggest other fed guilds do the same.  at any given opportunity, I am happy to host a practice session for CH rotation for all our clerics - even mebbe have a suicide attempt at Vindi just so u get the idea.<br>
